Ross Patterson, Dan Hollaway, and Dakota Meyer welcome special guest Mike Sarraille to discuss his book "The Talent War" about how to transition out of the military successfully into the business world.  He also discusses what it's like working for Jocko Willink, and Dakota Meyer joins us to chat about the election results.
